# Escape From The Maze - Project Overview

A party-based, first-person, phased-combat fantasy CRPG in Java 21 (AWT/Swing, no
game engine). Code namespace `mclachlan.*` under `src/maze/`. Built with Ant;
dependencies are vendored jars in `oem/`.

## The five major components

- **Game engine** - `src/maze/mclachlan/maze/game`, `.../map`, `.../stat`.
  `Maze` orchestrates; logic runs as `MazeEvent`s on one event thread.
- **Raycaster (Crusader)** - `src/maze/mclachlan/crusader`. Renders a zone map to
  an AWT `Image`. Game-agnostic.
- **UI framework (DIYGUI)** - `src/maze/mclachlan/diygui` (toolkit) +
  `src/maze/mclachlan/maze/ui/diygui` (game screens).
- **Persistence** - `src/maze/mclachlan/maze/data` (`Database` facade, `Loader`/
  `Saver`, V2 JSON serialisers).
- **Editor** - `src/maze/mclachlan/maze/editor/swing` (Swing content tool).

